The CFE-CGC is one of the 3 founding members of the Confédération Européenne des Cadres (CEC European managers). The CFE-CGC is also involved in European sectoral federations such as FECCIA, AECA, FECEC, FECC, FECER, Etic, FEDEM, FICT.&#xd;
&#xd;
Information about www.cec-managers.org&#xd;
&#xd;
The CFE-CGC is also a member of the International Confederation of Cadres (CIC), represented in the ILO since 1951. CFE-CGC is also member of the OECD Trade Union advisory Council and involved in the G20, G7, G8.
